<!-- Game Cheats Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Acquire Character Second Color -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Hold Select button, then press Circle. There are two colors for each character.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Setup Mode & Slow Motion -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">At the title screen where it tells you to "Press Start," enter the following code three times: Up, Up, Down, Down, Left, Right, Left, Right, X, Circle. You'll hear two sounds when you input it the first time and again when you input it the third. And yes, it's the classic Konami code.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Activate Setup Mode -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">After the above code is entered, press L1 during combat. Brackets will outline the characters. Blue brackets indicate where each character can be attacked. Yellow brackets indicate anything able to do damage. Transparent brackets indicate the full height of the character. Press L1 again to turn off Setup Mode.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Activate Slow Motion -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">After the above code is entered, press L2 during combat. The character will move at a much slower pace. Press L2 to turn off Slow Motion.</font>&nbsp;<br>
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">GAMESHARK CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Infinite HP Player 1 -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>801ED97C 00C0</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
	</table>
